::Teltoli::

She yelps as she sees the 45 shots heading towards them, and she 
yells Windlord to hang a hard right. They miss them and Teltoli pokes 
her tongue out at the two Alliance members, grinning smugly despite 
the sharp pain she was feeling.

'It'd be nice to fly with this Bot if we weren't being chased' 
Teltoli thought idly, and rested her head against Windlord's chest, 
hoping the Maximals replied to their plea in time. She didn't wanna 
die like this!
